# Your rule content

- You can not use import { useStrapi } from "@nuxtjs/strapi";
- Do not add classes or css unless I explicitly ask for it, and never add css inside a vue component.
- All interfaces are declared in the @types folder.
- Whenever persist is used in Pinia, it must always be validated using import.meta.client to make sure it's only run on the client side, especially when using localStorage.